          "q": "Do I have to pay to use the tree?",
          "a": "No. The tree, search, profiles, and export are entirely free. The aim of this project is to bring the family together, not to make money."
        },
        {
          "q": "What is support for, then?",
          "a": "Solely to help cover hosting costs. It's an optional gesture; nothing is ever locked away if you choose not to support."
        },
        {
          "q": "Can I stop my support at any time?",
          "a": "Yes. Cancellation takes effect at the end of the current period, and you keep exactly the same access as before: everything stays free."
        },
